   * Feed live updates to the system.
   * Run side-by-side simulation to show real improvements.

3. **Metrics to Track**

   * ğŸš† Section throughput â†‘ (trains handled/hour).
   * â±ï¸ Average train delay â†“.
   * ğŸ“Š Platform utilization â†‘.

